---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Morning Star Neuropathy & Pain Center in St. Peters, MO"
  description="Contact Morning Star in St. Peters, MO for neuropathy and pain treatment. Call (636) 244-0124 or visit us at 4710 Mexico Rd, Suite C."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy leading-tight mb-6">
        Contact Us
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Whether you are dealing with neuropathy, chronic pain, or a degenerative condition, our team is here to help. Reach out today to learn how Morning Star can create a personalized treatment plan for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact form + info -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Form -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Send Us a Message</h2>
        <form class="space-y-5" action="#" method="post">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" for="name">Name</label>
            <input
              id="name"
              name="name"
              type="text"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue"
              placeholder="Your full name"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" for="email">Email</label>
            <input
              id="email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue"
              placeholder="you@example.com"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" for="phone">Phone</label>
            <input
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              type="tel"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue"
              placeholder="(636) 555-0123"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="5"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue resize-none"
              placeholder="Tell us about your condition or questions..."
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full px-6 py-3 bg-brand-blue text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
          >
            Send Message
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact info -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Get in Touch</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-1">Phone</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">
              <a href="tel:6362440124" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">(636) 244-0124</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-1">Address</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">4710 Mexico Rd, Suite C</p>
            <p class="text-sm">St. Peters, MO 63376</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-1">Office Hours</h3>
            <p class="text-sm">Monday - Thursday</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-2">
            <a href="/schedule-appointment" class="inline-block px-6 py-2.5 bg-brand-blue text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              Schedule an Appointment
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-brand-navy mb-2">Can neuropathy symptoms be confused for other conditions?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Yes. Neuropathy symptoms such as tingling, numbness, burning sensations, and sharp pain in the hands or feet are frequently mistaken for other conditions including carpal tunnel syndrome, plantar fasciitis, restless leg syndrome, or even poor circulation. Many patients see multiple specialists before receiving an accurate peripheral neuropathy diagnosis. At Morning Star, we perform a comprehensive neurological evaluation to determine whether neuropathy is the underlying cause of your symptoms, ensuring you receive the correct treatment from the start.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-brand-navy mb-2">Can pain be treated without medication?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Absolutely. Morning Star specializes in non-pharmaceutical pain management. Our treatments include hyaluronic acid injections to lubricate and cushion damaged joints, platelet-rich plasma (PRP) therapy to accelerate tissue healing, exosome-based regenerative therapy to reduce inflammation, and neuromodulation to restore nerve function. These approaches target the source of your pain rather than masking it with medications, and many patients experience significant relief without ever taking a prescription pain reliever.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-brand-navy mb-2">What happens if neuropathy goes untreated?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Untreated neuropathy is a progressive condition, meaning it typically gets worse over time. Early symptoms like occasional tingling or mild numbness can advance to constant burning pain, severe loss of sensation, muscle weakness, balance problems, and increased risk of falls and injuries. In advanced stages, patients may develop foot ulcers, infections, and mobility limitations that significantly impact daily life. Early intervention offers the best opportunity to slow nerve damage, restore function, and prevent these serious complications.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-brand-navy mb-2">What should I expect at my first visit?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Your first visit to Morning Star begins with a thorough consultation. Our provider will review your complete medical history, discuss your current symptoms and pain levels, and perform a detailed physical and neurological examination. Depending on your condition, we may also conduct diagnostic testing to assess nerve function, joint integrity, or tissue health. Based on these findings, we will explain our diagnosis, discuss all available treatment options, and work with you to develop a personalized care plan. The initial visit typically takes 45 to 60 minutes, and you will leave with a clear understanding of your condition and a roadmap for your recovery.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-brand-navy text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Find Relief?</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200 mb-8">
        Call us at <a href="tel:6362440124" class="underline hover:text-white">(636) 244-0124</a> or schedule your appointment online. Our St. Peters, MO clinic is accepting new patients.
      </p>
      <a href="/schedule-appointment" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-brand-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">
        Schedule Appointment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
